          <div class="hidden md:block w-[45%] pl-12">
             <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Stress Test & Handoff</h3>
             <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Load testing, QA, and security validation. Once the platform meets our standards, we execute the final handover and server keys delivery.</p>
